query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('birt',
'bit-shift',
'dotnetnuke',
'ef-migrations',
'gtk3',
'jspdf',
'macos-sierra',
'nhibernate-mapping',
'stm32',
'tvos',
'v8',
'wrapper');
